{{italic title}}
'''''Ecos''''' is an online journal by the [[British Association of Nature Conservationists]] (BANC). The magazine was founded in 1974.<ref name=abec/> It was a print quarterly journal<ref>{{cite web|author=James Robertson|title=Obituary for ECOS - A Review of Conservation|url=http://www.maxnicholson.com/obituaries/ecos.htm|work=Max Nicholson|accessdate=26 September 2015}}</ref> until 2011<ref name=abec>{{cite news|title=About ECOS|url=http://www.ecosmagazine.com/nid/204.htm|accessdate=15 July 2016|work=ECOS}}</ref> when it went online.<ref name="banc">{{cite news|title=ECOS|url=https://www.banc.org.uk/ecos/|accessdate=15 March 2016|work=BANC}}</ref> The online journal is published three times a year.<ref name="banc"/> The journal publishes articles on [[conservation biology|nature conservation]]-related topics.

